{"tid":1164533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"承認涂謹申係合法主席，田北辰：政府直上大會係唔尊重立法會同民意","createTime":"2019-05-21T07:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T07:40:03.000Z","uid":157483,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9860105ba4b759023a4e954404b32665732ec1cc","tid":1164533,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:19:37.000Z","msg":"主要節錄：<br />\n「我地內會商討緊逃犯條例委員會既解決方法，我地立法會傾到一個方案出黎之前，政府都唔應該拎個法案上議會，呢個做法係唔尊重立法會亦都唔尊重民意，點解政府要咁急6月12號要通過？呢條法案咁大爭議，咁短時間草草咨詢根本就唔夠。」<br />\n「我地都未傾完個解決方案，點解繼續開法案委員會一定唔可行？<span style=\"color: red;\">可能涂謹申會自願辭職呢</span>，咁咪繼續開法案委員會囉。」<br />\n建制不嬲話泛民果個唔係會議，只係馬騮戲、飯盒會。田二少呢個講法即係endorse左阿涂係合法主席，如果唔係點存在請辭？田少好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比西環拆完天仲咁夠薑！希望到投票日田少都仲企硬投反對，繼承佢大佬23條人民英雄！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5xgLjtDAY5k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5xgLjtDAY5k&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=03a0b726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5xgLjtDAY5k</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n田北辰冇聯署DQ涂謹申主持人職務<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1148584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1148584</a>"},{"pid":"e9eb688f67b64b4e67ba7144c80dec75abe2df28","tid":1164533,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"261308d7438bcd65a293247b17c121d4dfe74ece","tid":1164533,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ac8c6a0b5a2b7a8d1fa2e39a6a0004ed087451","tid":1164533,"uid":157483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9eb688f67b64b4e67ba7144c80dec75abe2df28","tid":1164533,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T